<aside class="seatmap-side seatmap-side--left stage5-left">
    <div class="seatmap-side__title">STEP 05 · 예매 버튼 생성</div>

    <div class="seatmap-step-list">
        <section id="part1Panel" class="seatmap-step is-active" data-step="1">
            <button type="button" class="seatmap-step__header active" id="partBtn1">
                <span class="seatmap-step__check" data-step="1"></span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__text">
                    <b>파트 1</b>
                    <small>입력 데이터 확인</small>
                </span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__status" id="part1Status">진행중</span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__arrow">⌄</span>
            </button>

            <div class="seatmap-step__body">
                <div class="seatmap-step__system">
                    <div class="box active">
                        <h3>Stage 4 최종 산출물 확인</h3>
                        <div class="help-text">
                            Stage 5는 Stage 4의 최종 결과만 읽습니다. 기준 도면은 <b>seatmap-image.png</b>, 버튼 polygon 기준은 <b>seatmap-decorations.json</b> 입니다.
                        </div>

                        <div class="stage5-stat-grid">
                            <div class="stat"><b id="sectionCountText">0</b><span>section</span></div>
                            <div class="stat"><b id="seatCountText">0</b><span>seat</span></div>
                            <div class="stat"><b id="matchFailCountText">0</b><span>매칭 실패</span></div>
                            <div class="stat"><b id="missingNameCountText">0</b><span>이름 누락</span></div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="stage5-warning-list" id="warningList"></div>
                        <button type="button" class="btn primary" id="reloadDataBtn">입력 데이터 다시 읽기</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="part2Panel" class="seatmap-step" data-step="2">
            <button type="button" class="seatmap-step__header" id="partBtn2">
                <span class="seatmap-step__check" data-step="2"></span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__text">
                    <b>파트 2</b>
                    <small>버튼 자동 생성</small>
                </span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__status" id="part2Status">대기</span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__arrow">⌄</span>
            </button>

            <div class="seatmap-step__body">
                <div class="seatmap-step__system">
                    <div class="box active">
                        <h3>Stage 4 polygon → booking button</h3>
                        <div class="help-text">
                            버튼 polygon은 <b>referenceButtonPolygon → buttonPolygon → actualBounds → section polygon</b> 순서로 자동 생성합니다. 좌석은 다시 추정하지 않고 seatCount만 집계합니다.
                        </div>
                        <button type="button" class="btn green" id="generateButtonsBtn">booking button 자동 생성</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn" id="loadSavedButtonsBtn">저장된 booking-buttons.json 불러오기</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="part3Panel" class="seatmap-step" data-step="3">
            <button type="button" class="seatmap-step__header" id="partBtn3">
                <span class="seatmap-step__check" data-step="3"></span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__text">
                    <b>파트 3</b>
                    <small>전체 수정</small>
                </span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__status" id="part3Status">대기</span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__arrow">⌄</span>
            </button>

            <div class="seatmap-step__body">
                <div class="seatmap-step__system">
                    <div class="box active">
                        <h3>표시 옵션</h3>
                        <label class="stage5-check-row">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="showSectionPolygon">
                            <span>section polygon fallback 표시</span>
                        </label>
                        <label class="stage5-check-row">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="showButtonPolygon" checked>
                            <span>booking button polygon 표시</span>
                        </label>
                        <label class="stage5-check-row">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="showSeats">
                            <span>Stage 4 좌석 표시</span>
                        </label>
                        <label class="stage5-check-row">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="showLabels" checked>
                            <span>구역 label 표시</span>
                        </label>
                    </div>

                    <div class="box">
                        <h3>전체 수정</h3>
                        <div class="help-text">전체 글자 크기, 글자색, 버튼 투명도를 먼저 잡고 난 뒤 개별 구역을 수정합니다. 색상은 기본적으로 아래 PNG 구역색을 샘플링해서 polygon 색상과 맞춥니다.</div>
                        <div class="row stage5-control-row">
                            <div>
                                <label for="globalFontSizeInput">전체 글자 크기</label>
                                <input id="globalFontSizeInput" type="number" min="9" max="42" step="1" value="14">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label for="globalTextColorInput">전체 글자색</label>
                                <input id="globalTextColorInput" type="color" value="#1f2937">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stage5-field stage5-field--full">
                            <span>버튼 투명도 <b id="globalOpacityValue">100%</b></span>
                            <input id="globalOpacityInput" type="range" min="0.20" max="1" step="0.05" value="1">
                        </div>
                        <label class="stage5-check-row">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="syncStrokeFillInput" checked>
                            <span>polygon 색상과 최종 PNG 구역 색상을 동일하게 사용</span>
                        </label>
                        <div class="stage5-inline-actions stage5-inline-actions--triple">
                            <button type="button" class="btn" id="autoAllFontBtn">전체 글자 자동 맞춤</button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn" id="centerAllLabelsBtn">전체 label 중앙 정렬</button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn" id="resamplePngColorBtn">PNG 색상 다시 맞춤</button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn primary" id="applyGlobalBtn">전체 값 반영</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="part4Panel" class="seatmap-step" data-step="4">
            <button type="button" class="seatmap-step__header" id="partBtn4">
                <span class="seatmap-step__check" data-step="4"></span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__text">
                    <b>파트 4</b>
                    <small>선택 구역 수정</small>
                </span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__status" id="part4Status">대기</span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__arrow">⌄</span>
            </button>

            <div class="seatmap-step__body">
                <div class="seatmap-step__system">
                    <div class="box">
                        <h3>선택 구역 수정</h3>
                        <div class="help-text">도면에서 구역명을 드래그하면 labelPoint가 수정됩니다. polygon 꼭지점 편집 모드를 켜면 선택 구역의 꼭지점을 직접 드래그해 emergency 수정할 수 있습니다. 텍스트는 테두리 없이 단색으로 표시됩니다.</div>
                        <label class="stage5-field stage5-field--full" for="labelInput">
                            <span>버튼 명칭</span>
                            <input id="labelInput" type="text" placeholder="예: STANDING / VIP / D2">
                        </label>
                        <div class="row stage5-control-row">
                            <div>
                                <label for="fontSizeInput">글자 크기</label>
                                <input id="fontSizeInput" type="number" min="9" max="42" step="1">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label for="textColorInput">글자색</label>
                                <input id="textColorInput" type="color" value="#1f2937">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row stage5-control-row">
                            <div>
                                <label for="labelXInput">label X</label>
                                <input id="labelXInput" type="number" step="1">
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label for="labelYInput">label Y</label>
                                <input id="labelYInput" type="number" step="1">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row stage5-control-row">
                            <div>
                                <label for="colorInput">버튼 색상 / 찐 PNG 색상</label>
                                <input id="colorInput" type="color" value="#dbeafe">
                            </div>
                            <div class="stage5-help-mini">
                                선택한 색을 polygon fill과 최종 저장 PNG 색상에 같이 반영합니다.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <label class="stage5-check-row">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="vertexEditInput">
                            <span>polygon 꼭지점 편집 모드</span>
                        </label>
                        <div class="stage5-inline-actions">
                            <button type="button" class="btn" id="resetPolygonBtn">polygon 원본 복원</button>
                        </div>
                        <label class="stage5-check-row">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="visibleInput" checked>
                            <span>visible</span>
                        </label>
                        <label class="stage5-check-row">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="clickableInput" checked>
                            <span>clickable</span>
                        </label>
                        <div class="stage5-inline-actions">
                            <button type="button" class="btn" id="autoFontBtn">글자 크기 자동</button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn" id="applySelectedBtn">선택 구역 값 반영</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="box stage5-section-list-box">
                        <h3>booking button 목록</h3>
                        <div class="section-list stage5-button-list" id="buttonList"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="part5Panel" class="seatmap-step" data-step="5">
            <button type="button" class="seatmap-step__header" id="partBtn5">
                <span class="seatmap-step__check" data-step="5"></span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__text">
                    <b>파트 5</b>
                    <small>최종 저장</small>
                </span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__status" id="part5Status">대기</span>
                <span class="seatmap-step__arrow">⌄</span>
            </button>

            <div class="seatmap-step__body">
                <div class="seatmap-step__system">
                    <div class="box active">
                        <h3>최종 저장</h3>
                        <div class="help-text">저장 시 booking-buttons.json, 빨간 테두리 검수용 debug-polygons.png, Stage 6 꾸미기 전 최종 seatmap-stage5.png / seatmap-image.png를 함께 생성합니다.</div>
                        <div class="stage5-save-summary" id="saveSummary">저장할 버튼 0개</div>
                        <button type="button" class="btn green" id="saveBookingButtonsBtn">Stage 5 최종 저장</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn primary" id="toStage6Btn">Stage 6 최종 꾸미기로 이동</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</aside>

<main class="seatmap-main stage5-main" id="canvasScroll">
    <div class="canvas-wrap stage5-canvas-wrap">
        <div class="canvas-head">
            <strong id="canvasTitle">예매 화면 버튼 미리보기</strong>
            <span id="canvasSize">-</span>
        </div>
        <div class="canvas-box stage5-canvas-box" id="canvasBox">
            <canvas class="base" id="stage5BaseCanvas"></canvas>
            <canvas id="stage5OverlayCanvas"></canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="stage5-tooltip" id="stage5Tooltip"></div>
    </div>
</main>

<aside class="seatmap-side seatmap-side--right stage5-right">
    <div class="minimap">
        <h3>원본 미니맵</h3>
        <img id="miniImg" alt="seatmap-image 미니맵" />
        <div class="help">Stage 4 최종 <b>seatmap-image.png</b>를 우선 사용하고, 없으면 seatmap-stage5.png / button-image.png / cropped-image.png 순서로 표시합니다.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="preview-card stage5-preview-card">
        <h3>찐 저장 미리보기</h3>
        <canvas id="previewCanvas"></canvas>
    </div>

    <div class="preview-card stage5-info-card">
        <h3>선택 구역 정보</h3>
        <dl class="stage5-info-list">
            <div><dt>sectionId</dt><dd id="infoSectionId">-</dd></div>
            <div><dt>sectionName</dt><dd id="infoSectionName">-</dd></div>
            <div><dt>층 / 등급</dt><dd id="infoFloorGrade">-</dd></div>
            <div><dt>가격</dt><dd id="infoPrice">-</dd></div>
            <div><dt>좌석 수</dt><dd id="infoSeatCount">-</dd></div>
            <div><dt>예매 가능</dt><dd id="infoAvailableCount">-</dd></div>
            <div><dt>labelPoint</dt><dd id="infoLabelPoint">-</dd></div>
            <div><dt>visible / clickable</dt><dd id="infoFlags">-</dd></div>
        </dl>
    </div>

    <div class="preview-card">
        <h3>JSON 미리보기</h3>
        <pre class="json-box" id="jsonPreview">[]</pre>
    </div>
</aside>
